        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>CISA Leadership Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a term limit and specifies the appointment process for the Director of the Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency (CISA) of the Department of Homeland Security. </p> <p>Specifically, the bill establishes a five-year term for the director of CISA.</p> <p>The director shall be appointed by the President, by and with the advice and consent of the Senate.]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
